{"tid":2417503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"確診者曾到灣仔警總　警方：逗留時間短　會如常辦公","createTime":"2021-02-22T02:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T13:55:52.000Z","uid":239336,"like":279,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"c467b33fc326ffe5dff134146df620ba435c0a77","tid":2417503,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"一名曾經到訪灣仔警察總部的公眾人士，確診感染武漢肺炎。警方昨社交網站表示，該名確診者周三曾到訪警察總部 14 樓申請紀錄查核，辦公室已設置透明隔板，所有職員都有戴口罩，而有關公眾人士在大樓逗留的時間較短，到訪的範圍較小，因此警察總部會如常辦公。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，高度關注事件，在等候衛生署進一步評估和建議前，會安排可能與確診者有密切接觸的人員做檢測；警方亦已派員清潔和消毒地方，並會調派人手，確保服務不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-確診者曾到灣仔警總-警方-逗留時間短-會如常辦公/?fbclid=IwAR36GbXQ9Fsr8qosaV2HNWQfPY1Qev4hzV1Vrnjg27wK0x8X2L5j5Nb_6ng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E9%80%97%E7%95%99%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E7%9F%AD-%E6%9C%83%E5%A6%82%E5%B8%B8%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR36GbXQ9Fsr8qosaV2HNWQfPY1Qev4hzV1Vrnjg27wK0x8X2L5j5Nb_6ng&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=28909cf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E9%80%97%E7%95%99%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E7%9F%AD-%E6%9C%83%E5%A6%82%E5%B8%B8%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR36GbXQ9Fsr8qosaV2HNWQfPY1Qev4hzV1Vrnjg27wK0x8X2L5j5Nb_6ng&h=2fb9e9ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-確診者曾到灣仔警總-警方-逗留時間短-會如常辦公/?fbclid=IwAR36GbXQ9Fsr8qosaV2HNWQfPY1Qev4hzV1Vrnjg27wK0x8X2L5j5Nb_6ng</a>"},{"pid":"8274c76ea2da143ec87be3cc4d14bdded6f0d207","tid":2417503,"uid":37739,"like":116,"dislike":0,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"正確<img src=\"/assets/faces